</ul>

<p>
  A great tool for testing .NET code snippets, LINQ statements, etc. is <a href="http://www.linqpad.net/" target="_blank">LINQPad</a>. 
  This little application is extremely feature packed and you'll find more ways to use it every time you open it.
</p>

